HEADWORD: Protocercal
<hw>Pro`to*cer"cal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Proto-</ets> + Gr. <?/ the tail.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Having a caudal fin extending around the end of the vertebral
column, like that which is first formed in the embryo of fishes;
diphycercal.</def>⟦br⟧
